org.afplib.afplib

Interface IPG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IPGImpl

    public interface IPG
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'IPG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pg Name
    • IPg Flgs
    • Triplets

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getIPG()
